Campbell's.

50:23.920 --> 50:27.014
Sure. Actually, I'm not allowed
to sell alcohol at this hour.

50:27.190 --> 50:30.159
You promise not to tell the boss?
I promise.

52:11.895 --> 52:14.329
What were you lookin' at, Jimmy?

52:16.166 --> 52:18.293
What were you lookin' at?

55:56.486 --> 55:58.977
Somebody answer for Christ's sakes!

56:01.725 --> 56:03.556
Answer!
State Police here.

56:03.693 --> 56:06.662
Hello? Hello, police?
Oh I beg of you, help me!

56:07.230 --> 56:09.198
Okay, calm down
and tell me what the problem is.

56:09.299 --> 56:11.631
The Sorals, they have a farm
near Puyanne.

56:11.768 --> 56:13.668
I'm a friend of their daughter
Alexis.

56:13.770 --> 56:16.671
This guy broke in during the night.
He broke in and he murdered everyone!

56:16.773 --> 56:19.571
He took my friend away
in a pickup truck
and I'm really afraid for her.

56:19.676 --> 56:21.010
He just killed the gas station guy.

56:21.010 --> 56:22.312
Gas station?
Yes.

56:22.312 --> 56:23.711
You're in a gas station?

56:23.813 --> 56:25.405
Yes.
Which gas station?

56:31.788 --> 56:33.312
Hold on. I'll have a look.

56:38.395 --> 56:40.420
I don't know what station.
I was in his pickup truck.

56:40.530 --> 56:42.862
All I know is it's a very old pickup
brown, old and rusty.

56:42.966 --> 56:45.059
Did you get
the vehicle's plate number?

56:45.168 --> 56:47.568
How could I get the number?
I told you I was inside the truck!

56:47.670 --> 56:49.638
Do you realize how many pickup trucks
there are on the road?

56:49.739 --> 56:51.707
Without a plate number...
Jesus, an old pickup truck

56:51.808 --> 56:54.936
on a country road at this time
of night shouldn't be that hard
to spot, huh?!

56:55.044 --> 56:58.138
Calm down please, ma'am
and tell me where you are.

56:58.481 --> 57:01.712
Listen, this son of a bitch just
took off with her. If you don't send
someone right now

57:01.818 --> 57:03.285
she'll never make it!

57:03.420 --> 57:05.888
I understand, but we can't help you
if we don't know where you are.

57:05.989 --> 57:10.085
If I burn this damn gas station down
maybe you can locate it, huh?!

57:18.568 --> 57:22.698
The keys... they keys...

01:00:14.077 --> 01:00:16.671
Where does the murdering
son of a bitch live?

01:02:22.238 --> 01:02:23.603
Shit!

01:02:26.776 --> 01:02:28.539
Where did he go...

01:10:12.875 --> 01:10:15.105
Why'd ya care so much about Alex?

01:10:15.678 --> 01:10:21.617
She turns you on?
She does same to me.
She turns me on too.

01:13:01.310 --> 01:13:05.542
The lights are all out.
It looks shut down for the night.
Better have a look.

01:13:14.456 --> 01:13:16.356
Go around the back, Fred.

01:13:16.825 --> 01:13:18.690
And be careful, huh?
Right, Captain.

01:13:35.010 --> 01:13:38.173
Captain, the back door is locked.
We've gotta...

01:13:38.680 --> 01:13:40.545
Y'better call headquarters.

01:13:45.187 --> 01:13:49.851
This is patrol car 214 calling.
We've got a murder victim here.

01:14:03.772 --> 01:14:05.000
Oh my God!

01:14:27.896 --> 01:14:29.363
It's me, Alex. It's me.

01:14:36.605 --> 01:14:38.596
It's over.

01:14:42.744 --> 01:14:44.109
It's all over.

01:15:26.355 --> 01:15:27.379
Okay.

01:15:28.657 --> 01:15:30.090
Don't touch me!

01:15:30.792 --> 01:15:32.419
Don't touch me I said!

01:15:33.228 --> 01:15:35.253
It's all over. He's dead.

01:15:35.397 --> 01:15:36.999
He's dead. It's over.

01:15:36.999 --> 01:15:40.059
You don't make any sense!
Get away!

01:15:40.168 --> 01:15:42.329
It's all over, all over.
Back off!

01:15:43.238 --> 01:15:45.069
Alex, calm down.
Back off!

01:15:49.378 --> 01:15:51.676
It's over, Alex.
I killed him. He's dead.

01:15:54.049 --> 01:15:58.713
Alex, please calm down.
Back off! Don't come closer!

01:15:58.820 --> 01:16:03.382
Alex, come. It's all over now.
He can never do anything again.

01:16:03.926 --> 01:16:07.157
You mad bitch! I'm gonna cut
your head into pieces!

01:16:07.296 --> 01:16:11.289
It's me, Marie, your friend.
I'm on your side!

01:16:11.433 --> 01:16:13.867
I killed him, Alex.
It's finished. He's dead.

01:16:14.436 --> 01:16:17.405
You murdered my whole family!
You murdered my whole family!

01:16:17.506 --> 01:16:20.737
You don't know what you're saying.
There was nothing I could do
to save them.

01:16:20.909 --> 01:16:22.467
There was just you.
You know that.

01:16:22.578 --> 01:16:26.173
Alex, everything's gonna be okay
from now on.

01:16:26.281 --> 01:16:31.309
Please, you've gotta trust me, Alex.

01:17:06.755 --> 01:17:09.656
You'll pay for this, you bitch!

01:17:21.003 --> 01:17:23.335
I'm gonna take care of you, Alex!

01:17:30.912 --> 01:17:32.880
I'm gonna take care of you, Alex!

01:17:56.672 --> 01:18:00.005
Help me! Help! Help me!

01:18:03.512 --> 01:18:04.979
Go on! Go! Hurry!

01:18:05.113 --> 01:18:06.580
What's going on?
Hurry!

01:18:06.682 --> 01:18:10.743
Hurry up! Go go! Go on!

01:19:13.915 --> 01:19:15.644
I'll tear your head off!

01:20:51.346 --> 01:20:54.474
You wanna drive me crazy
you god damn bitch, huh?

01:20:56.218 --> 01:20:57.913
No... No...

01:21:00.755 --> 01:21:02.222
Do ya love me?

01:21:03.325 --> 01:21:04.883
You don't love me.

01:21:07.128 --> 01:21:08.959
Y'don't love me, do ya?

01:21:17.772 --> 01:21:23.108
You don't love me.
Yes, yes!

01:21:23.445 --> 01:21:33.548
Yes, I love you! Yes
I do love you! I love you!

01:22:20.268 --> 01:22:26.332
Nobody'll come between us
ever again, Alex...
Never again...

01:22:27.709 --> 01:22:33.341
I won't let anyone come
between us anymore...

01:22:36.251 --> 01:22:40.347
